@startuml uml_class_notification
title LLD — notification-service (HTTP + gRPC — proto/notification.proto)
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica

package "HTTP / worker transport" {
  class "HTTP / worker\nhandlers (server.ts)" as Http <<Node>>
  class "NotificationService\n(grpc-server.ts)" as Grpc <<Node>> {
    GetUserPreferences()
  }
}

package "Application" {
  class "Notification\norchestrator" as S <<service>>
}

package "Infrastructure" {
  class "Persistence\n(Postgres / Prisma)" as R <<repository>>
  class "Kafka consumer\n+ optional outbox" as K
}

Http --> S
Grpc --> S
S --> R
K --> S
S --> K

note bottom of Grpc
  **Contract:** `proto/notification.proto`
  — **no** SendNotification RPC; delivery
  is **triggered from Kafka** events only.
end note

@enduml
